      <scopecontent id="aspace_65e93a5fc2484aad11bc6d86dcf7a5e5">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of minutes, correspondence, reports, and personnel files documenting personnel, teaching appointments, curriculum, the American Numismatic Society, and the Board of Permanent Officers of the Yale Department of Classics.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
